##TABLE_START &#9679; Data and access solutions &#8211; includes access and capacity fees, proprietary market data fees, and associated other revenue across Cboe&#8217;s six segments. ##TABLE_END &#8203; 

##TABLE_START &#9679; Derivatives markets &#8211; includes associated transaction and clearing fees, the portion of market data fees relating to associated U.S. tape plan market data fees, associated regulatory fees, and associated other revenue from Cboe&#8217;s Options, Futures, Europe and Asia Pacific, and Digital segments. ##TABLE_END &#8203; 

