##TABLE_START &#9679; Royalty fees and other cost of revenues &#8211; includes royalty fees and other cost of revenues across the Company&#8217;s six segments. In prior periods, royalty fees and other cost of revenues were presented as distinct cost of revenues categories. ##TABLE_END &#8203; 

